window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Gangsters, aristocrats, offworlders . . . What difference does it make? To Mikhail Bulatov, none whatsoever. Any of them could be friend or foe, and he could care less what world they're from or what their place is in the social order.</p> <p>As for his enemies, any conversation will be equally brief, even if different in content. And yes, those out to get him are ramping up their efforts, and increasing in number. Not that there's any question of his ability to handle it all.</p> <p>That being said, he must not lose sight of who he is. First and foremost, he is a Healer.</p>"; 
